title: Advantage Browns or Broncos? Biggest game of Joe Burrow's career? National Tight End Day; Survival; Dawuane Smoot
itunes:title: Advantage Browns or Broncos? Biggest game of Joe Burrow's career? National Tight End Day; Survival; Dawuane Smoot
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Cris Carter share which team has the advantage in Thursday's must win game between the injury plagued Cleveland Browns and the banged up Denver Broncos. Then they get into 'would you rather' questions focused on Lamar Jackson and Joe Burrow; they celebrate National Tight End's day with trivia; they share their survival picks and lastly, they're joined by Dawuane Smoot and his wife to share the incredible story of their baby girl's birth.
